rows.label: tlk70000013_05_msg0001
rows.name:
Did I just hear you say the name
"Macmac"? I've never met her myself,
but she sounds like quite the character.

rows.label: tlk70000013_05_msg0002
rows.name:
Why, she smacked Chairman Morumo
right on his fluffy little arse!

rows.label: tlk70000013_05_msg0003
rows.name:
No idea how it happened. Not sure I
want to know, either... Truth is I'm
afraid to ask.
